Class Airplane

      • Airplane

        public Airplane(java.lang.String make,
                java.lang.String model,
                int capacity,
                AirplanePilot pilot)
        Constructor for the Airplane object receiving its make (or brand), its model, its maximum capacity and an AirplanePilot object.
        Parameters:
        make - holds the brand of the airplane.
        model - holds the model of the airplane.
        capacity - holds the maximum number of passengers of the instance of the Airplane object.
        pilot - holds an object AirplanePilot which is assigned to the instance of the Airplane object.
